Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情回顾\N{\fs12}previously on The Guardian
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你偷了我的信用卡吗  香农\N{\fs12}You stole my credit card, Shannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是嗨了吗\N{\fs12}You stone right now？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这很有意思吗\N{\fs12}Do you think this is funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  你一直以来对我帮助很大  对我们都很大\N{\fs12}You know you been very helpful to me, to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再多留两周吧\N{\fs12}Stay on for two more weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  但我只是\N{\fs12}I'm sorry, but I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我做不到\N{\fs12}I mean...I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,香农现在会怎么样\N{\fs12}What happens to Shannon now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想做寄养家长  是有一整套流程要走的\N{\fs12}If you want to be a foster parent, there's a whole procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  是你一开始想让我离开的\N{\fs12}You know you are the one who wants me to leave in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在的情况变了  露露\N{\fs12}Our situation here has changed Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我有父亲的\N{\fs12}You know... I have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想确认一下你知道  这一切都是暂时的\N{\fs12}Just want to make sure you know this is just temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放松点儿  尼克\N{\fs12}Take it easy, Nike
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我被要求离职了\N{\fs12}I been asked to resign my position here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,立即生效\N{\fs12}effective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给了我给你工作\N{\fs12}I been offered your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受了\N{\fs12}I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你知道\N{\fs12}So you know the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃  这就意味着  - 是\N{\fs12}- Uh, this means I'm your... - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿现在你说了算了\N{\fs12}You are in charge here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你能处理得好吗\N{\fs12}And you can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  伯顿\N{\fs12}Morning, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  小花生\N{\fs12}Hey, Peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我说早上好\N{\fs12}l said good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚叫我小花生\N{\fs12}You called me Peanut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是爱称  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Term of endearment, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这不是\N{\fs12}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不能抽  你也不能\N{\fs12}lf I can't, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}Oh. I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的书忘在楼上了\N{\fs12}l left my book upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早上好  露露  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Good morning, Lulu. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你  呃  那是给  我的案子吗\N{\fs12}Do you, uh-- Is that case for, uh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗\N{\fs12}Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,新办公室\N{\fs12}New omice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,萨曼莎·格雷  十二岁\N{\fs12}Samantha Gray, 12 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在尝试为她建立待命监护人\N{\fs12}We're trying to establish a standby guardian for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试\N{\fs12}Trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  社会服务  有人\N{\fs12}Yeah--Social Services, someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是她妈妈  弄砸了\N{\fs12}maybe the mom, kind of dropped the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么需要一个待命监护人\N{\fs12}Why do you need a standby guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她妈妈生病了  因为针头感染了艾滋\N{\fs12}Her mother's sick. She contracted AIDS through a needle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们现在要将萨曼莎托付给她妈妈的最好的朋友吗\N{\fs12}so we're trying to transition Samantha to the mother's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她妈妈的朋友叫安吉拉·埃弗斯  资料里都有写\N{\fs12}Her name's Angela Evers. It's all in the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你需要让这位妈妈填好文件\N{\fs12}So, you'll need the mom to fill out the paperwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要让埃弗斯夫人签字\N{\fs12}and you'll need Mrs. Evers' signature also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她妈妈在哪里\N{\fs12}Where will I find the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瓦利赛德安养院  - 安养院  不去\N{\fs12}- Valleyside Hospice. - Hospice? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须拿到签字\N{\fs12}You've got to get a signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不去  - 为什么\N{\fs12}- No. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是\N{\fs12}l just--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  别啊  这是我的与第一天啊\N{\fs12}Nick, come on. It's my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个案子  你需不需要\N{\fs12}That case--do you need to--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  尼克可以搞定\N{\fs12}No, no, Nick's got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要怎么做\N{\fs12}How do you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我想我也在试着弄清楚\N{\fs12}l don't know. I just want to try to figure it out, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去看看旧的案子\N{\fs12}I'll just go through the old cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,清理下文件柜\N{\fs12}weed out the filing cabinets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下  我找安吉拉·格雷\N{\fs12}Excuse me. I'm looking for Agnes Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  抱歉\N{\fs12}Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她的房间在那里\N{\fs12}Uh, that's her room over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,您是格雷女士吗\N{\fs12}Mrs. Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,您好  我叫尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Hi. My name is Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边有份文件需要您签字\N{\fs12}l have a form here for you to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我把它放在这里了\N{\fs12}All right, I'll put the form here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟护士说一下\N{\fs12}and I'll tell the nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名片放在文件的上方\N{\fs12}My business card is on the top of the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,热水\N{\fs12}The hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,您说什么\N{\fs12}Mrs. Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,额  文件放在这儿了  我的\N{\fs12}Uh, OK. The form's here, and my--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fs12}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是护士吗\N{\fs12}Are you the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我的朋友丹尼来一杯威士忌\N{\fs12}Another whiskey for my friend Danny,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请再给我来点咖啡\N{\fs12}and some more coffee for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道事情的总和总是大于它每个部分的\N{\fs12}l don't know that the sum of the thing is bigger than its parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就说得通了\N{\fs12}but it adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  一个小孩死了\N{\fs12}l mean, a kid dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人会说我的行为需要负责  对吗\N{\fs12}Some people would say my actions were responsible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个决定从来没有被考虑进\N{\fs12}But that decision could never have taken into account
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来发生的事情中去\N{\fs12}the events that followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对  所以\N{\fs12}Right? So--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其他事情就会发生\N{\fs12}And then, so, other things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就像死亡是随机的  暴力也是\N{\fs12}Like deaths that are random and violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我打一个人  也是随机的\N{\fs12}And me hitting some guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再想想  我想我在\N{\fs12}And, again, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这些事情中的位置\N{\fs12}about my part in these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有和露露的其他事\N{\fs12}And another thing-- with Lulu--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,事实是  她就是她\N{\fs12}the fact that she is how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在她变成了我的老板\N{\fs12}And now she's my boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,混了这么多年  我应该向\N{\fs12}And I'm supposed to, after all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,像她这种人报告吗\N{\fs12}report to someone like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  再一次  我是一个想为孩子辩护的律师\N{\fs12}But, then again, I am a lawyer who wants to advocate for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  还有机会\N{\fs12}And, uh, I still have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每当我走进那个地方的时候\N{\fs12}But every time I walk into that place--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便一提  是我我一手建造的\N{\fs12}which, by the way, I created--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在被告知要接管另外一个女人的办公室\N{\fs12}and I'm told to take over another woman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  我必须\N{\fs12}l think I must--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须对这一切说不\N{\fs12}l must say no to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗\N{\fs12}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我错了\N{\fs12}Or am I wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没错\N{\fs12}Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要再来一杯\N{\fs12}You would like another drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天怎么不说话\N{\fs12}You've been very, very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的建议吗\N{\fs12}My solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我知道你的建议\N{\fs12}Heh. I think I know your solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,去跑步吧\N{\fs12}Go to the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伦森夫人  阿伦森先生\N{\fs12}Mrs. Aaronson, Mr. Aaronson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲告诉我\N{\fs12}Your father told me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这些案子你有一套自己处理的方法\N{\fs12}that you knew your way around these kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我熟悉抚养权的问题\N{\fs12}l am familiar with custody issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想起诉\N{\fs12}We want to sue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Oh. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在那个诊所花了成千上万元\N{\fs12}We spent thousands of dollars at that clinic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,受了很多苦\N{\fs12}undeM/ent painful procedures,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们却用错误的精子给我太太的卵子受精\N{\fs12}and they fertilized my wife's egg with the wrong sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是我的精子给错误的卵子受精  或者两者都搞错了\N{\fs12}Or...my sperm with the wrong egg. Or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也做了一些研究  有其他案例可循\N{\fs12}We've done the research. There have been other cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲说你们想留下孩子\N{\fs12}My father said that you wanted to keep the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们应该为他们犯的错付出代价\N{\fs12}But they should pay for their mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,诊所那边有没有联系你们解决问题\N{\fs12}Has the clinic contacted you about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们否认自己做错事\N{\fs12}They denied they did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我太太每天都熬夜看着小孩\N{\fs12}My wife is up nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,生怕有人会来抢走她的小孩\N{\fs12}afraid that someone is going to take her baby away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,法律上来讲  如果是她生出了这个孩子\N{\fs12}Well, by law, if she carried the child
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个孩子就属于她\N{\fs12}the child is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以追究这家诊所的医疗事故\N{\fs12}We can go after the clinic with medical malpractice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,以及这期间遭受的痛苦的责任\N{\fs12}pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们需要做一些基本的测试\N{\fs12}But you will have to do some basic tests
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,确定孩子与两位的亲子关系\N{\fs12}to determine paternity or maternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了吗亲爱的  我就说他们不能这么对我们\N{\fs12}See, honey? I told you they can't just do this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以让助理把验血的文件拿给你\N{\fs12}l can get my paralegal to get you the forms for the blood work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我来把您的投诉信息整合一下\N{\fs12}and I will work on putting together your complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能认识两位\N{\fs12}lt's really nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好萨曼莎\N{\fs12}Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字叫尼克\N{\fs12}My name is Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\fs12}l remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈去世的时候你就在房间\N{\fs12}When my mom died, you were in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我错过了\N{\fs12}l missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该陪着她的\N{\fs12}l was supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过她会握紧她的手\N{\fs12}l promised her that I'd hold her hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样她就不会害怕了\N{\fs12}so she wouldn't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有握住她的手  对吗\N{\fs12}You didn't hold her hand, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}Uh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  当然  你怎么会呢\N{\fs12}Right, of course. Why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来害怕吗\N{\fs12}Did she seem scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,萨曼莎  在法庭上\N{\fs12}Samantha, in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要给你找一个住的地方\N{\fs12}we need to find you a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我会搬去跟安吉一起住\N{\fs12}l thought I was going to stay with Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不  呃\N{\fs12}No. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她不知道这个计划\N{\fs12}she was not aware of that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她改变主意了吗\N{\fs12}She changed her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  你妈从来没有跟她谈过这个事\N{\fs12}No, your mother never asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好吧\N{\fs12}Oh. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道还有其他可以收留你的家庭\N{\fs12}Do you have any other family that could take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲在哪里\N{\fs12}What about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我父亲是谁\N{\fs12}l don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你父亲的名字吗\N{\fs12}Do you know his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了我不知道我的父亲是谁\N{\fs12}l don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要去法庭了  你可以处理下这个吗\N{\fs12}I'm due in court now. Could you please handle this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,处理完之后打我办公室的电话\N{\fs12}and call me at my office later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你稍等一会儿\N{\fs12}Just wait here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 劳瑞  - 尼克\N{\fs12}- Laurie. - Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她父亲怎么回事  - 什么\N{\fs12}- What's going on with her father? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,萨曼莎·格雷  那个失明的女孩\N{\fs12}Samantha Gray, the blind girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我查不到她父亲的任何信息\N{\fs12}l can't find anything out about the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为他的父亲权利被终止了\N{\fs12}That's because his parental rights were terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前海洛因上瘾  八年前有次吸嗨了\N{\fs12}He was a heroin addict. He got high,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了一起交通事故\N{\fs12}there was a car accident about eight years ago--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,正面碰撞\N{\fs12}a head-on collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他害死了那个司机  自己的女儿也瞎了\N{\fs12}He killed the other driver and caused his daughter's blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他作为父亲的权利被终止了\N{\fs12}So, his rights were terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把她送到哪里去\N{\fs12}Where do you want to send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大都会医院的特殊需求之翼\N{\fs12}The Special Needs Wing of Metropolitan Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  萨曼莎·格雷没有精神疾病\N{\fs12}Your Honor, Samantha Gray isn't mentally ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是对于一个十四岁的失明女孩来说\N{\fs12}There is simply nothing else available
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有其他办法\N{\fs12}for a 14-year-old girl with Samantha's disability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那盲人学校呢  - 没有愿意收的\N{\fs12}- What about the school for the blind? - There are no openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  因为都是私立的吗\N{\fs12}What, because it's private?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是钱的事情\N{\fs12}This is not about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想知道你有没有把所有可能性都考虑过了\N{\fs12}l would just like to know that you have exhausted all other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在努力寻找一个合适的寄养家庭\N{\fs12}We are trying to locate an appropriate foster family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,或者一个特殊的教养院\N{\fs12}or a special needs group home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  大都会精神病院\N{\fs12}Your Honor Metropolitan Psychiatiic Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不适合萨曼莎·格雷去\N{\fs12}is not an appropriate placement for Samantha Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,绍尔特小姐  你确定没有其他选择了吗\N{\fs12}Miss Solt, you are confident there are no alternatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时是的\N{\fs12}Yes, I am, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我裁定萨曼莎暂时\N{\fs12}I'll adjudicate Samantha dependant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,去大都会精神病院30天\N{\fs12}and place her in Metropolitan for 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在下个月去拜访她\N{\fs12}We'll revisit her placement next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去大都会精神病院什么意思\N{\fs12}What does that mean, ''dependant''?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,意思就是你现在受国家监护\N{\fs12}lt means that you're a ward of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,国家的监护\N{\fs12}Ward of the state?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大都会医院的埃文斯先生来接萨曼莎了\N{\fs12}Mr. Evans is here from Metropolitan to take Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,劳瑞会照顾你的\N{\fs12}Uh, Laurie's going to take care of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去哪里  - 有我在  亲爱的\N{\fs12}- Where am I going? - I'm here, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟劳瑞和埃文斯先生走\N{\fs12}You'll go with Laurie and Mr. Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是埃文斯先生  - 谁是埃文斯先生\N{\fs12}- This is Mr. Evans. - Who's Mr. Evans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他是大都会医院来的\N{\fs12}He's here from Metropolitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该去跟安吉住的\N{\fs12}I'm supposed to go with Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带我去哪里  我要跟安吉一起住\N{\fs12}Where are you taking me? l want to go with Angie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你不能跟安吉住\N{\fs12}Sweetheart, you can't go with Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我  不 我要跟安吉住\N{\fs12}Let go of me! No, I want to go with Angie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  先生  打扰一下  先生\N{\fs12}Sir? Sir? Excuse me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩  萨曼莎·格雷  他们要送她去哪里\N{\fs12}That girl--Samantha Gray-- where are they sending her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们昨天在安养院见过  我告诉你艾格尼丝的房间在哪里\N{\fs12}l met you yesterday at the hospice. l showed you where Agnes' room was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  对  谢谢\N{\fs12}Oh, right. Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要把萨曼莎送哪里去\N{\fs12}Where are they sending Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么认识萨曼莎·格雷\N{\fs12}How do you know Samantha Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只是比较感兴趣  - 你是谁\N{\fs12}- I'm just interested. - Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她父亲\N{\fs12}I'm her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫吉姆·格雷\N{\fs12}Jim Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她\N{\fs12}She's, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她在这个世界上无依无靠了\N{\fs12}l mean, she's all alone in the world--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是抱歉格雷先生  你的抚养权被终止了\N{\fs12}Well, I'm sorry, Mr. Gray, but your parental rights have been terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道\N{\fs12}Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只是  我听到艾格尼丝的事情之后就开始做准备了\N{\fs12}lt's just... I started making preparations when I heard about Agnes--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我无能为力\N{\fs12}As long as you understand there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你的抚养权被终止了\N{\fs12}Your parental rights have been terminated. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊一聊吧\N{\fs12}Just talk to me for a second--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了你\N{\fs12}There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在有个不错的公寓\N{\fs12}I've got a nice apartment now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一份工作  我工作很努力\N{\fs12}And I got a good job. I'm working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不能跟我聊一下吗\N{\fs12}Can't you just talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的宝贝女儿啊\N{\fs12}She's my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  至少我希望你能把她送到一个不错的地方\N{\fs12}Well, I hope you at least send her to someplace nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来找香农的\N{\fs12}I'm here to see Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你是她朋友吗\N{\fs12}Oh, are you a friend of hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我叫汉克  我应该帮她学几何的\N{\fs12}Yes, sir. I'm Hank. I'm supposed to help her with some geometry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有提起过这事儿\N{\fs12}She didn't say anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天才商量好的  她当时在做足球练习\N{\fs12}Oh, we just talked about it today. She was at soccer practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她  额  她现在有点不舒服\N{\fs12}She's, uh-- She's not feeling well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她的身体\N{\fs12}She's got a little problem that makes her feel, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不舒服\N{\fs12}not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会告诉她你来过了  - 好的\N{\fs12}- I'll tell her you came by. - Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫汉克  是吧  - 对\N{\fs12}- Hank, right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你要工作到很晚吗\N{\fs12}You're working late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我第一天上班  额\N{\fs12}So, my first day was, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  对  今天感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}Oh, right. How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我太累了\N{\fs12}Heh. I think I'm in over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚跑完步回来\N{\fs12}I'm back from the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加班到很晚  再查查这个案子\N{\fs12}I'm going to stay late, go over some of this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪  有些孩子  你会忘记\N{\fs12}You know, it's amazing-- some of these kids. You forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要加班到很晚吗\N{\fs12}You going to work late, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  也许我们可以  呃\N{\fs12}Well, maybe we could, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去吃点东西\N{\fs12}go get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点饿了\N{\fs12}I'm kind of hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是找我的\N{\fs12}That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么出来的\N{\fs12}How did you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有看着我\N{\fs12}They weren't watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看不到\N{\fs12}Because I'm blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没想到我就这样走出来了\N{\fs12}They didn't think I'd just walk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,医院里很吵\N{\fs12}lt's very loud at Metropolitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以听到有些孩子\N{\fs12}l could hear the kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他人  在尖叫\N{\fs12}and other people, screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,比在安养院的时候更糟糕\N{\fs12}lt was worse than at the hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,更糟糕\N{\fs12}lt was worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我就往外面走  直到安静了\N{\fs12}l walked till it was quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果法官知道你一个人跑出来了\N{\fs12}Well, the judge isn't going to be very happy to know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,会很高兴的\N{\fs12}that you ran away from Metropolitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有疯\N{\fs12}I'm not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想回去\N{\fs12}l don't want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没疯\N{\fs12}I'm not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你及时赶来了  法林先生\N{\fs12}Appreciate you coming in so promptly, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望今天就能搞定这事儿\N{\fs12}We're hoping to put this to rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到了检测结果的复印件以及你的控诉\N{\fs12}l received a copy of the test results, along with your complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fs12}We're--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,测试结果表明我的客户生出的孩子\N{\fs12}The tests indicate that my client gave birth to a baby that--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,基因跟母亲有关\N{\fs12}That is genetically related to the woman, the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是跟父亲无关\N{\fs12}but not to the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她在你们的诊所进行了体外受精\N{\fs12}She undeM/ent in vitro fertilization in your clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后生出来一个一半非洲一半美国血统的孩子\N{\fs12}and gave birth to a child that is half-African-American.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她在程序中的时候并未怀孕\N{\fs12}She didn't get pregnant from that procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她是在那之后怀孕的\N{\fs12}She got pregnant after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,之后\N{\fs12}After?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到布拉克斯顿医生的记录时就会发现\N{\fs12}That's what you'll find when we produce Dr. Braxton's records.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这家诊所没有非洲裔男人\N{\fs12}There haven't been any African-American men in this clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  很有意思的是  如果你好好想想这类事情\N{\fs12}Actually, it's interesting, if you care to think about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是接受了手术\N{\fs12}She must have undergone the procedure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了延迟排卵  然后\N{\fs12}had a delayed egg release, and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以证明你们没有雇用过非洲裔男人\N{\fs12}You can prove you've never had an African-American client?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉克斯顿医生的诊所收集精子都是严谨有记录的  法林先生\N{\fs12}Dr. Braxton's clinic doesn't draw sperm from the general public, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  你好\N{\fs12}Nick, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须等保姆回来我才能出门  不好意思\N{\fs12}l had to wait for the nanny to get back, so...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}lt's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要事跟我说吗\N{\fs12}You needed to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝点什么吗\N{\fs12}Yeah. Do you want a drink or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  现在不用\N{\fs12}Oh, no. I'm not, um-- Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,杰基  这些测试\N{\fs12}Jackie, those tests--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,测试出来你是孩子的生母\N{\fs12}it turns out that you are the biological parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来一点也不惊讶  是吧\N{\fs12}lt doesn't surprise you that you are the mother of the child, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不惊讶\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我来一杯加冰伏特加\N{\fs12}Uh, could I have a vodka rocks, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上去见了布拉克斯顿医生和他的律师\N{\fs12}l met with Dr. Braxton and his attorney this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关于你的诉讼  - 嗯\N{\fs12}- Regarding your lawsuit. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有诉讼了  - 嗯\N{\fs12}- There is no lawsuit. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是在程序之后才怀孕的  所以\N{\fs12}Because you got pregnant after the procedure. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在我联系你的丈夫之前  我想我们应该先聊一下\N{\fs12}before I contacted your husband, l thought that we should talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能不告诉我丈夫吧\N{\fs12}We couldn't just keep this between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那样会很难\N{\fs12}That would be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格雷先生  这是  - 吉姆\N{\fs12}- Mr. Gray, this is-- - Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们见过\N{\fs12}We met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是劳瑞·索尔特\N{\fs12}This is Laurie Solt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷先生  我是你  我是萨曼莎的社会工作者\N{\fs12}Mr. Gray, I'm your-- Samantha's social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以  她现在在哪儿  - 她在一个收容所\N{\fs12}- So, where is she? - She's in a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收容所\N{\fs12}Shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她在大都会精神病院\N{\fs12}She's at Metropolitan Psychiatric Facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她发生什么事了吗\N{\fs12}Did something happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  她很好\N{\fs12}No, she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只是暂时没有更合适的地方了\N{\fs12}There's just no other alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有经常去看她\N{\fs12}You know, um, l would've seen her lots and lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我从监狱一出来之后就经常去看她\N{\fs12}Once I got out of prison and all that, l was going to see her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我和这座城市  - 城市怎么了\N{\fs12}- but me and the city-- - The city?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不回来匹兹堡了  我做不到\N{\fs12}l don't come to Pittsburgh anymore. l can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你现在来了  - 是的\N{\fs12}- You're here right now. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我来了\N{\fs12}That's right. I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷先生  关于你的要求\N{\fs12}Mr. Gray, about your request--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你该被允许收养你的女儿呢\N{\fs12}why should you be allowed to adopt your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是戒毒两年的纪念币\N{\fs12}That's a two-year coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我戒毒成功了\N{\fs12}I'm clean, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很遵纪守法了  我戒毒成功了  你明白吗\N{\fs12}l have been good. I'm clean, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个不错的工作和一个不错的公寓\N{\fs12}l have a good job, a nice apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我去教堂做礼拜\N{\fs12}l go to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我住在贝德福德县  在高速公路部门工作\N{\fs12}l live down in Bedford County, work for the highways,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一天要干很长时间  很累\N{\fs12}put in long hours, it tires me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我回到家之后就直接睡觉  就这样\N{\fs12}l come home, go to bed, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,教堂  圣经  床  我过得不错\N{\fs12}Church, bible, bed. l have been good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当我听到艾格尼丝的事情之后  我之前很爱很爱她\N{\fs12}And when I heard about Agnes-- who I loved very much--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始计划\N{\fs12}l started to make plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs12}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是社会服务的女士写的\N{\fs12}this is what the Social Services lady wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她来我住的地方看了\N{\fs12}when she came out to see my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看  这儿\N{\fs12}Look, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可接受\N{\fs12}''Acceptable.''
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是贝德福德县\N{\fs12}This is Bedford County.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这个和潜在收养可能没有任何关系\N{\fs12}lt doesn't have anything to do with the potential adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个是一份家庭调查\N{\fs12}But it's a home study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是由一个专业人士  像您一样的专业人士给出的\N{\fs12}l mean, by a professional, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷先生  我已经做社会工作有30年了\N{\fs12}Mr. Gray, I've been a social worker for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年来  我很少推荐\N{\fs12}ln that time, I've recommended
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,终止抚养权\N{\fs12}very few terminations of parental rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这就相当于判了死刑\N{\fs12}lt's the legal equivalent of a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗  终止\N{\fs12}Do you understand? Termination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,法庭很明确的认为你女儿不跟你生活会更好\N{\fs12}The court clearly thought your daughter would be better om without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道您说的意思\N{\fs12}l understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您明白吗  我已经改过自新了\N{\fs12}Do you understand that I've changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,填下申请表吧\N{\fs12}Fill out the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前是瘾君子  我那个时候情况很糟\N{\fs12}l was a junkie, you know? Yes, and I was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs12}Yes, but that--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你需要雇一个律师\N{\fs12}Right, so, you're going to need to hire a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前是有问题\N{\fs12}l had problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那并不表示我不爱我的太太和女儿\N{\fs12}But that does not mean I didn't Iove my wife and or my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我挺了过来  我已经得到了应有的惩罚\N{\fs12}And I lived with that, and I have made most of my amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我来这里想要把我的宝贝女儿接回去\N{\fs12}And I am here to get my little girl back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要代表自己\N{\fs12}lf you're going to represent yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你填写这些文件\N{\fs12}then I will help you fill out the forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的名片  好吗\N{\fs12}Here's my card. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,萨曼莎怎么样了\N{\fs12}How's Samantha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她看上去不错\N{\fs12}Well, she seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  我之前会去安养院看她\N{\fs12}You know, I'd watch her at the hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她看上去已经不是个小女孩了\N{\fs12}She doesn't even look like a little girl anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你会告诉她这件事吗\N{\fs12}So, are you going to tell her about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,会的  她是我的客户\N{\fs12}Yes, she's my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  祝你好运\N{\fs12}Well, good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在高中教英文\N{\fs12}You taught English in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,九年级和十年级\N{\fs12}Ninth and tenth grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你有个儿子\N{\fs12}You have a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,安东尼  19岁  在高露洁上班\N{\fs12}Anthony, 19. He attends Colgate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很优秀  好的好的\N{\fs12}Oh, excellent. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你做\N{\fs12}So, how many, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你做保姆几年了\N{\fs12}how many years have you been a nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,三年\N{\fs12}Three years. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在做的这家有一对双胞胎男孩\N{\fs12}l was working with twin boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,自荐信就在我给您的文件夹里\N{\fs12}The reference letter is in the folder I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  恕我冒失\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, I don't mean to be presumptuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我想知道想下父母对保姆的期望\N{\fs12}but I like to know what the parents' expectations are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,期望\N{\fs12}Expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  香农是您收养的孩子\N{\fs12}Well, Shannon's your foster child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,您不知道她会跟您住多久\N{\fs12}You don't know how long you're going to have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在来到了一个新的家庭  一个新的学校\N{\fs12}She's in a new home, a new school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fs12}l just--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是担心会增加新的元素\N{\fs12}I'm just concerned about adding yet another element.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你  海伦娜\N{\fs12}Well, I appreciate that, Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是我想要找的人\N{\fs12}But, uh, you're the one I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  开个价吧  你什么时候可以开始就通知我一下\N{\fs12}So, just name your price, Iet me know when you can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是钱的问题\N{\fs12}lt's not just about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  就先见一见香农吧\N{\fs12}Well, then come meet Shannon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证  你会很喜欢她的\N{\fs12}and I promise you, you'll love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以保证你\N{\fs12}l can promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲现在住在匹兹堡\N{\fs12}Your father is in Pittsburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我父亲吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- My father? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他过来见我了吗\N{\fs12}He came here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要收养你\N{\fs12}Uh, he wants to try and adopt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样\N{\fs12}What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  他看起来  他在努力\N{\fs12}Well, he seems like he's-- he's trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我能见见他吗\N{\fs12}Can I see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,萨曼莎  你对你父亲知道多少\N{\fs12}Samantha, how much do you know about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈跟我讲他是个瘾君子\N{\fs12}My mother said that he was a drug addict,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不见也是他造成的\N{\fs12}that he made me blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道他的抚养权被终止了\N{\fs12}Do you understand that his parental rights have been terminated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  没人告诉我\N{\fs12}No. No one told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这就意味着  从法律上来说他已经不是你父亲了\N{\fs12}That means that legally he isn't your dad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能收养我吗\N{\fs12}lt's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他已经改过自新了\N{\fs12}Even if he's changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,极有可能\N{\fs12}lt's highly unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,即使也许我想跟他住吗\N{\fs12}Even if I maybe wanted him to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己说了你不了解你父亲\N{\fs12}You said yourself you don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你了解\N{\fs12}Even if you did--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  你没有理由去相信\N{\fs12}What I mean to say is, there's no reason to believe--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是\N{\fs12}Right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但你觉得  我能见见他吗\N{\fs12}do you think that l could just see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你无缘无故给了她新的希望\N{\fs12}You're getting her hopes up for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有法官会撤回终止的\N{\fs12}No judge is going to overturn a termination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得这个人值得我们花时间\N{\fs12}Why do you even think this guy is worth our time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,劳瑞\N{\fs12}Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\fs12}Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿了  - 马场  怎么了\N{\fs12}- Where have you been? - The track. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有新的案子给我妈\N{\fs12}You got a case for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  法林先生  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hey, Mr. Fallin. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这些  呃\N{\fs12}These, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这些你给我的关于收养的文件  我真的搞不懂\N{\fs12}These forms you gave me for the adoption stuff are really confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格雷先生  我们刚刚见了  - 叫我吉姆好了\N{\fs12}- Mr. Gray, we just met-- - Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆  好的吉姆  我们刚刚见了莎曼萨  她答应见你了\N{\fs12}Jim. Jim, we just met with Samantha. She's agreed to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候  - 明天下午\N{\fs12}- When? - Tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这  这真是太棒了\N{\fs12}That is-- This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  谢谢你  这意味着还有希望  对吗\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thank you. l mean, this means something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味她同意见见你\N{\fs12}Well, it means that she's agreed to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  我不知道说什么了\N{\fs12}This is great. l don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我填下这些文件吗\N{\fs12}Could you help me with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先不急  我们先见见她再说吧  好吗\N{\fs12}Not yet. Let's just meet with her and see what happens, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  只是这里面要写一片文章\N{\fs12}OK, yeah. It's just-- one of them is this essay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我为什么要当她的父亲  但是我就是她的父亲  对吗\N{\fs12}about why I want to be her dad. And I am her dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得就是要解释下事情的来龙去脉\N{\fs12}lt's about explaining myself, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我相信你可以的  - 你这样认为吗\N{\fs12}- I'm sure you'll do fine. - You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  谢谢你\N{\fs12}OK, well...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去喝杯咖啡\N{\fs12}Do you want to grab a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得回去工作了\N{\fs12}l have to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:23:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  谢谢你  还有  法林先生\N{\fs12}OK, all right. Thank you. And, Mr. Fallin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道附近有没有那种会\N{\fs12}do you know where there's a meeting around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种  大家好  我叫吉姆  我是个瘾君子的会\N{\fs12}You know, ''Hi, my name is Jim. I'm a drug addict.''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得第五大道的加略教堂\N{\fs12}l think there may be one on 5th,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有一个\N{\fs12}at the old Calvary Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.86,0:24:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}OK, I appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  法林先生  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you, Mr. Fallin, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.18,0:24:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,周五晚上乡村俱乐部有重大活动\N{\fs12}Big doings at the country club Friday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.84,0:24:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.57,0:24:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每年一届的父女舞会\N{\fs12}Annual Father-Daughter Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我预定了\N{\fs12}l made reservations...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.57,0:24:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想去的话\N{\fs12}if you're game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟汉克说了什么\N{\fs12}What did you tell Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fs12}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.68,0:24:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,汉克  之前来过这里的男孩\N{\fs12}Hank, that boy who came over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他我来例假了是不是\N{\fs12}You told him about my period, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我身体不舒服  但是我没有不舒服\N{\fs12}You said I wasn't feeling good. l was feeling fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.15,0:24:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  亲爱的\N{\fs12}You know what, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.67,0:25:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前一直没跟你说\N{\fs12}And I should've told you this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.66,0:25:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得你的生活里需要一个女人\N{\fs12}But I think that you need a woman in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.19,0:25:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去倾诉  去帮你完成作业  去做饭给你吃\N{\fs12}to talk to, help you with your homework, cook for you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.32,0:25:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs12}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我在说要请一个保姆\N{\fs12}I'm talking about a nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.52,0:25:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保姆  - 是的\N{\fs12}- A nanny? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午我面试了一个年轻的女士\N{\fs12}And this afternoon l interviewed a young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.83,0:25:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她棒极了\N{\fs12}and I think she's absolutely terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  我觉得是她来了\N{\fs12}Guess what? I think that's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.76,0:25:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我只是想让你见见她  好吗\N{\fs12}Honey, I just want you to meet her, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你喜不喜欢她  好吗\N{\fs12}See if you like her, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能过来\N{\fs12}Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.04,0:25:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,香农  跟海伦娜打声招呼\N{\fs12}So, Shannon, say hi to Helena.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.51,0:25:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是香农\N{\fs12}This is Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.88,0:25:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴  香农\N{\fs12}lt's a pleasure to meet you, Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.81,0:25:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,海伦娜以前是个教师\N{\fs12}Helena was a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.70,0:25:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有很多事她可以帮你\N{\fs12}l thought maybe she could help you with some things, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.48,0:26:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早上好  尼古拉斯  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Nicholas, good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.29,0:26:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有\N{\fs12}Did, uh, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.34,0:26:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们昨晚有没有聊聊目前的情况\N{\fs12}Did the two of you have a chance to discuss your situation last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.95,0:26:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我就就是为此而来\N{\fs12}That's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.31,0:26:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伦森夫人  你有没有\N{\fs12}Mrs. Aaronson, did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  就是一些正常的对话\N{\fs12}Not really, just regular talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.65,0:26:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}OK, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.50,0:26:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想介入个人的问题\N{\fs12}l don't like to be in the middle of a person matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.49,0:26:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  阿伦森先生  事情有了新的进展\N{\fs12}But, Mr. Aaronson, there's been a development--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.41,0:26:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想要留下宝宝\N{\fs12}We want to keep our baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.30,0:26:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以整件事都太愚蠢了\N{\fs12}So, this whole suit thing-- it's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么进展\N{\fs12}What's the development?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.49,0:26:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我们回去吧\N{\fs12}Honey, come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,整件事都太蠢了  我都不知道我们为什么来这里\N{\fs12}This whole thing is so stupid. l don't even know what we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.49,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说的进展事是什么\N{\fs12}No. What's the development?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.38,0:26:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得阿伦森夫人想要说的是\N{\fs12}l think what Mrs. Aaronson is trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.08,0:26:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这件案子再追究下去没有意义\N{\fs12}is that she doesn't think this suit makes sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.09,0:26:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 怎么了  杰基\N{\fs12}- OK. - What, Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.80,0:26:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怀孕了  - 我知道你怀孕了\N{\fs12}- I got pregnant. - You got pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.01,0:26:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在我去诊所之后\N{\fs12}After I went to the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.71,0:26:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 之后  - 跟另外\N{\fs12}- After. - With another--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.34,0:27:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟别人有了孩子\N{\fs12}You got pregnant with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.81,0:27:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁的孩子  - 阿尔伯特\N{\fs12}- Whose baby is it? - Albert--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.02,0:27:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是谁的\N{\fs12}Whose baby is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.45,0:27:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我们不能对诊所提起诉讼了  所以\N{\fs12}I'm sorry. Uh, we no longer have a claim against the clinic, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.65,0:27:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱恩  埃丝特  鲍勃\N{\fs12}Elaine. Esther. Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.39,0:27:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道今天有股东大会啊\N{\fs12}l didn't know there was a board meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.64,0:27:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吧  很搞笑\N{\fs12}You know, it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.56,0:27:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看了这些旧的案子  让我想到\N{\fs12}Looking at these old cases makes me wonder--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.54,0:27:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有让事情变得有所不同吗\N{\fs12}did we make a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.01,0:27:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我们可以吗\N{\fs12}I mean, Ã§an we make a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是蝴蝶的翅膀吗  我们是风吗\N{\fs12}Are we butterfly wings? Are we the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.90,0:27:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就想是马一样\N{\fs12}lt's like the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.53,0:27:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,会去弄清楚  那条道才是最适合自己的路\N{\fs12}You try to figure out which one's the best fit for the track,
