Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.19,0:27:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以会议之后再说这些  接下来交给我吧\N{\fs12}We can talk after the meeting. l can take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.53,0:28:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你会  呃\N{\fs12}Yeah, you'll, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,给你半小时  差不多吗\N{\fs12}Give you, what, a half hour or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.27,0:28:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多\N{\fs12}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.52,0:28:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我应该那个时候就不在了\N{\fs12}Right. Uh, I might be gone by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.86,0:28:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也许还在\N{\fs12}But, uh, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.74,0:28:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再看吧\N{\fs12}Let's just see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  再看吧\N{\fs12}Right. Let's just see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.94,0:28:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  这篇关于为什么我想成为萨曼莎的父亲的文章\N{\fs12}Now, this essay about why l want to be Samantha's dad.
