Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.11,0:28:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我要去马场上了\N{\fs12}l think I'm going to head out to the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能不能跟露露说一下  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Mind telling Lulu for me? - OK.
