Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得阿尔文是想让我解雇他\N{\fs12}l think that Alvin's trying to get me to fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.64,0:29:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就解雇啊\N{\fs12}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.49,0:29:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在忙那件案子吗  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Are you busy with that case? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.93,0:29:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我听说那个女人死的时候你在场\N{\fs12}Well, I heard that woman died when you were there.
