Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.70,0:29:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.23,0:29:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别  别停啊  刚刚跳得很好  亲爱的\N{\fs12}No, don't stop. That was excellent, sweetheart.
