Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去  做作业了  好吗\N{\fs12}I've got to-- My homework, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.43,0:29:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}OK.
