Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.79,0:30:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,探索真理的方式  是啊\N{\fs12}A way with the truth, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.39,0:30:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说  如果你想知道现在是不是太\N{\fs12}Listen, if you're asking me if it's too...
