Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,永远 永远不会\N{\fs12}Never. Never that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你愿不愿意留下来\N{\fs12}So, you want to-- you want to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.83,0:30:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我愿意  - 很好\N{\fs12}- Yes. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.01,0:30:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.89,0:30:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.09,0:30:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她呀  呃\N{\fs12}She's, um--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.41,0:30:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她对这次的舞会很激动\N{\fs12}she's really excited about this dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.00,0:30:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起出去  穿上新的裙子\N{\fs12}A night out with you, a new dress.
