Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.63,0:31:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要叫我爸爸还是吉姆\N{\fs12}Do you want to call me Dad or Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs12}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.72,0:31:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得叫你爸爸挺好的\N{\fs12}l think Dad's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.16,0:31:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.70,0:31:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那我叫你什么  萨曼莎还是萨姆\N{\fs12}And you? Um, are you Samantha or Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.74,0:31:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我萨曼莎吧\N{\fs12}Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.37,0:31:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你越长越漂亮了\N{\fs12}You've just--you've just grown up so beautifully, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.68,0:31:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 对啊\N{\fs12}- I have? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.66,0:31:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看看我的样子  我长得很呆蠢  哈哈\N{\fs12}You should see me. I'm kind of goofy-looking? Ha ha!
