Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.74,0:31:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得妈妈长得漂亮吗\N{\fs12}You think Mom was pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.08,0:31:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  她很漂亮  真的很漂亮\N{\fs12}Yes, she was. She was really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.97,0:31:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你介不介意我\N{\fs12}Do you mind if l--
