Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.53,0:31:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs12}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错嘛\N{\fs12}You're not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.18,0:32:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一双眼睛  一个鼻子  一张嘴巴\N{\fs12}l got both my eyes, my nose, my mouth.
