Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.88,0:32:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  让我说  让我说\N{\fs12}Well, let me--let me--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你变成这样都是我造成的\N{\fs12}l did this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.17,0:32:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果最后没有成功的话\N{\fs12}And if nothing else comes of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你能听到我对你有多抱歉\N{\fs12}at least you can finally hear me say how sorry I am.
