Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.87,0:32:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你明白吗  - 我明白\N{\fs12}- Do you understand? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.09,0:32:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好听证会了吗\N{\fs12}Are you ready for the hearing?
