Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有必要的话  我不想待在匹兹堡了\N{\fs12}and I just don't want to be in Pittsburgh any longer than I have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.17,0:33:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这件事没那么快\N{\fs12}l don't think we can get it done that fast.
