Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.15,0:33:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只是\N{\fs12}lt's just--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.53,0:33:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不\N{\fs12}l don't know. I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.82,0:33:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前就是经常这样想自己的\N{\fs12}This is how I used to think about myself, I know.
