Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.01,0:33:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经变好了  对吗\N{\fs12}Because I'm better now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.95,0:33:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以的  我是她爸爸  我可以的\N{\fs12}l can do this. I'm her daddy. l can do this.
