Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.12,0:33:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  很便宜的\N{\fs12}Not really, but it's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.04,0:33:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,从贝德福德来这里要两个小时\N{\fs12}l live two hours away from here-- you know, in Bedford.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.67,0:33:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道吗  - 不知道\N{\fs12}- Do you know it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.14,0:33:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,贝德福德很不错的\N{\fs12}Bedford's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.06,0:33:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很安静  很平和\N{\fs12}lt's quiet, it's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.48,0:33:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要上来  可以看个电影\N{\fs12}Do you want to come up for a while, maybe watch a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.93,0:34:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不用\N{\fs12}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.01,0:34:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  我可以请你吃晚饭\N{\fs12}l, uh-- l can buy you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.86,0:34:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,街那头有个很不错的餐厅\N{\fs12}There's a nice diner down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.99,0:34:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去参加一个\N{\fs12}There's a meeting I go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.44,0:34:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在加略教堂的会\N{\fs12}over at the Calvary Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.71,0:34:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 八点开始\N{\fs12}- What? - It starts at 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.81,0:34:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.74,0:34:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.85,0:34:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  被你抓到了\N{\fs12}Oh, Burton, you caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.35,0:34:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不  没关系的\N{\fs12}Oh, no, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.21,0:34:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,香农上楼了  我吸根烟\N{\fs12}Shannon was upstairs, so I snuck a butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.04,0:34:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Oh, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.54,0:34:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还有烟吗  - 当然\N{\fs12}- You got another one? - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.24,0:34:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  伯顿\N{\fs12}Hey, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  听我说\N{\fs12}Oh, honey, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.54,0:34:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个客户出了点问题  今晚可能有点麻烦\N{\fs12}one of my clients has a problem, so tonight might be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.64,0:34:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去的\N{\fs12}I'm going to be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.25,0:34:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是可能会晚几分钟  - 哦\N{\fs12}- but just maybe a few minutes late. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.71,0:35:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在好消息是尼克会把你送过去的\N{\fs12}Now, the good news is Nick is going to be able to drive you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.69,0:35:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克吗  - 是\N{\fs12}- Nick? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.22,0:35:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在我没去之前  他会当你的护花使者的\N{\fs12}He's going to be your escort until I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎样  今天都会玩得很开心的  好不好\N{\fs12}You're going to have fun all the way around, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.03,0:35:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 就这样\N{\fs12}- Yeah. - All righty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.57,0:35:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿见\N{\fs12}See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.08,0:35:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.05,0:35:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要见我吗\N{\fs12}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.33,0:35:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.71,0:35:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一些关于阿伦森太太的坏消息\N{\fs12}Some bad news about Aaronson's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.50,0:35:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 发生了一起事故\N{\fs12}- What happened? - There was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他对她做了什么\N{\fs12}What did he do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.92,0:35:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像发生了争吵\N{\fs12}lt seems there was an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.49,0:35:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她从楼梯跌了下去\N{\fs12}She fell down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.99,0:35:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在她跌倒之前  头部可能受过打击\N{\fs12}Potentially a blow to the head before she fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.53,0:35:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吗\N{\fs12}Potentially?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.16,0:35:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 目前还没有证据  - 那她还好吗\N{\fs12}- I don't have all the facts yet. - Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.59,0:35:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好  她的脑部伤得很严重\N{\fs12}No, she's badly hurt. Her brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经逮捕了阿尔伯特\N{\fs12}They already arrested Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.82,0:35:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经派克莱和萨迪去了  我还是要亲自去一趟\N{\fs12}l sent Clay and Sadie down there. I'll have to go down there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.57,0:35:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应香农\N{\fs12}l promised Shannon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.43,0:35:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我会带她去俱乐部的父女舞会的\N{\fs12}I'd take her to the Father-Daughter Dance at the club tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.89,0:35:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道那边需要忙多久  我会跟阿尔伯特待一起  所以\N{\fs12}l have no idea how long I'll be with Albert, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.29,0:35:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别啊  爸  别  别\N{\fs12}Oh, Dad, Dad--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.63,0:35:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你先送她去  我会赶过去\N{\fs12}Just drive her over there, and I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.48,0:36:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是开车送过去  对吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- Just drive her there? - Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.20,0:36:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就要轮到萨曼莎的案子了\N{\fs12}Samantha's case is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.05,0:36:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.43,0:36:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪儿\N{\fs12}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.06,0:36:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.66,0:36:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.74,0:36:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,到她了\N{\fs12}she's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.01,0:36:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你待在这儿没事吧\N{\fs12}will you be OK here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.87,0:36:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他住的宾馆离这里只有一条街  我去去就回\N{\fs12}His hotel room is just a block away. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.60,0:37:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟到了\N{\fs12}I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.83,0:37:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你父亲回家了\N{\fs12}Your-- Your dad went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.70,0:37:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  呃\N{\fs12}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.82,0:37:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你下一场听证会是在28天后\N{\fs12}your next hearing is in 28 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.76,0:37:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.16,0:37:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候我们再帮你搬地方\N{\fs12}And we will get you moved then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.14,0:37:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,28天\N{\fs12}28 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.11,0:37:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  28天后我们帮你搬地方\N{\fs12}That's when we'll move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.08,0:38:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过了\N{\fs12}You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.77,0:38:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伦森先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Aaronson.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}Hello, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你在外面看到你父亲了吗\N{\fs12}Did you see your dad outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.57,0:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  看到了\N{\fs12}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.35,0:38:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伦森先生  呃\N{\fs12}Mr. Aaronson, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.47,0:38:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,关于萨拉\N{\fs12}about Sarah--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.64,0:38:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,萨拉吗\N{\fs12}Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.85,0:38:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的孩子\N{\fs12}Your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.32,0:38:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有人照顾她吗\N{\fs12}ls there anyone that can take care of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.33,0:38:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她有保姆照顾\N{\fs12}She's with a nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.60,0:38:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但是法律上来讲  她的生父有权利\N{\fs12}Well, legally, the biological father has rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.99,0:38:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗\N{\fs12}He does?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,法律上有\N{\fs12}Legally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:39:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我准备好帮助你了  如果你\N{\fs12}But I'm prepared to help you if you--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.71,0:39:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.77,0:39:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想把她留下的话\N{\fs12}lf you wish to keep her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.21,0:39:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.81,0:39:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  不用\N{\fs12}Thank you, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.99,0:39:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过孩子的爸爸了吗\N{\fs12}Have you met the father?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.19,0:39:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟我说他们只是朋友\N{\fs12}She said they were just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.88,0:39:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至在我的一个商店给了他一份工作\N{\fs12}l even gave him a job at one of my stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.91,0:39:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了那家伙一份工作\N{\fs12}l gave that guy a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.06,0:39:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  阿尔文\N{\fs12}Oh, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.25,0:39:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要去马场\N{\fs12}I'm on my way to the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.49,0:39:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我目前已经赚了3000了  不可思议\N{\fs12}I'm up $3,000 so far-- an astonishing run.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你要搞清楚如果你选择不去完成你的工作的话\N{\fs12}Alvin, understand that if you choose not to do your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.23,0:39:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我就得\N{\fs12}then I will have to--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.35,0:39:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  解雇我吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- What? Fire me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.69,0:39:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我  露露  我相当于已经被解雇了\N{\fs12}I've already been fired, Lulu, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.96,0:40:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这个地方已经相当于一个死人了\N{\fs12}I'm already dead to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.59,0:40:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  这是谁的宝宝\N{\fs12}Nick. Whose baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.74,0:40:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是莎拉·阿伦森\N{\fs12}This is Sarah Aaronson.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.69,0:40:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他的生父不想要他\N{\fs12}The biological father doesn't want her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.60,0:40:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈去世了  我得走了\N{\fs12}Mother's dead. I've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  你好\N{\fs12}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.79,0:40:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs12}Yeah, it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.48,0:40:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帮我联系下社会服务  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Call Social Services. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.37,0:40:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这儿建一个收容所\N{\fs12}I'll set up a shelter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.23,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是最后一曲了\N{\fs12}l think this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.09,0:40:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.48,0:41:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意\N{\fs12}You know, uh, if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.00,0:41:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以陪你跳最后一支舞\N{\fs12}l can dance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.78,0:41:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意的话\N{\fs12}lf you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs12}Come on.
